function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/123995/', '', 'Felodipine, Amlodipine, Verapamil, Bisoprolol, Hydrochlorothiazide, Indapamide', 'Tapentadol, Naloxone, Dezocine, Oxymorphone, Acamprosate, Varenicline, Disulfiram, Levacetylmethadol, Nalmefene, Nicotine, Dexfenfluramine, More', 1767369485);
